{"tid":616465,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建制「冧友」增法定人數要求種惡果","createTime":"2018-04-04T07:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T15:32:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"918aa3b46d196340582909f7a9f910aaa3c0bf52","tid":616465,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T07:50:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180404/20351581\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180404%2F20351581&d=EQeDkbj5XTFf33Q5RgtclRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=6f4e662d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180404%2F20351581&h=17c6658f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180404/20351581</a><br />\n<br />\n建制「冧友」增法定人數要求種惡果<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180404/large/04ls2p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180404%2Flarge%2F04ls2p2.jpg&h=89104816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葉劉淑儀為開快車配合政府審議，一個半月之內召開13次會議。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【拆局】<br />\n<br />\n為配合政府對廣深港高鐵香港段於今年第三季通車的期望，建制派早前「冧友」加入一地兩檢法案委員會，務求爭奪委員會的控制權和主席職位，加快審議進度。但此舉同時令法定人數的要求提高，在建制派不願乖乖開會的情況下流會機會大增；加上主席葉劉淑儀罕有在復活節與清明節假期之間召開會議，釀成流會惡果建制有一定責任。<br />\n<br />\n《議事規則》規定，法案委員會的法定人數為委員人數的三分之一，一地兩檢法案委員會的人數多達64人，法定人數多達21人。建制派方面，除了立法會主席梁君彥、廖長江、鍾國斌、潘兆平，其他40人都是委員會委員，最終建制冧友成功令「心儀」的葉劉和張國鈞可以順利當選正副主席。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假期開會　多人外遊<br />\n<br />\n惟根據過往經驗，不少議員都會在「冧友」、完成選舉主席程序後退出委員會，不過由於一地兩險委員會對港府、中央政府而言都是重中之中，無人輕言退會，令法定人數仍然在高水平之上。<br />\n<br />\n再加上，委員會主席葉劉淑儀為開快車配合政府審議，一個半月之內召開13次會議，就連議員多數會外遊的復活節假期都要用到盡開會，最終建制派昨日只有18人在席，石禮謙、黃定光等人都在外遊，令泛民偷襲成功釀成流會。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳嘉裕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t政府證大律師公會指法案違《基本法》<br />\n港聞 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t【蘋果照相機】點解會流會？<br />\n港聞 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t一地兩檢流會　葉劉即安排周日加會陳淑莊：為配合通車死線漠視違憲<br />\n港聞 5小時前"},{"pid":"3e5cef4a4d63d1f78c123aaa0d23032a823b7b79","tid":616465,"uid":93784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T07:52:36.000Z","msg":"去旅行緊要啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa82bce8d8c43f4fecaf2ddeb2db07eafa66567","tid":616465,"uid":20227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T07:52:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9b65fc2040336565de5da26482876966fc602a0","tid":616465,"uid":3454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T07:53:37.000Z","msg":"上次修改議事規則又唔修埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f9ae4423d5a53c78233607cd58b1a79e15f7b74","tid":616465,"uid":56533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T07:59:16.000Z","msg":"豬隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個諗住自己友會頂，然後走晒去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4ed7a15cd0132f92c4876d21095eeb4f2327ce","tid":616465,"uid":176366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:30:50.000Z","msg":"記得今次呢件事cctvb都有報<br />\n<br />\n最尾泛民講咗句：「如果唔係建制配合，我地都會成事。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"054cf36e7ba